{"tid":565791,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]前新華社香港分社副社長張浚生逝世","createTime":"2018-02-19T10:28:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-20T10:35:03.000Z","uid":1251,"like":65,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"b1ea308c794e5395e6b030958aebe43057566f55","tid":565791,"uid":1251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T10:28:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/posts/803588199833250\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ficablenews%2Fposts%2F803588199833250&d=dPt5hoR%2F8%2FipJ5OUgle%2BkIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=9fcbb763\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/posts/803588199833250</a><br />\n<br />\n新年流流<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9ef22e61bb92d9f4c7617876af2c9d1ee1ee3c0","tid":565791,"uid":51271,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T10:30:14.000Z","msg":"老毛又召見一個"},{"pid":"8775bd5c4ce660efe7dece0a60eebd180223ccf6","tid":565791,"uid":162424,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T10:30:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"93e9d6f3c18ca567074a93a49997e77f2c22c33f","tid":565791,"uid":103230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T10:32:04.000Z","msg":"黃子華成日抽佢水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c6008e23a21201f4e35c019f3fe189043600f06","tid":565791,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T10:36:16.000Z","msg":"【張浚生病亡】曾嘲港青於基本法起草時「細胞還未形成」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n報道指，新華社香港分社前副社長張浚生在內地病逝，終年82歲。2016年旺角騷亂後，張接受電視訪問時形容，該次騷亂是暴動，顯示港府教育青年人不足，加上港青受外部勢力策動，由前年開始的政改爭論，可看到港青不理解《基本法》，盲目行動，笑謂「《基本法》起草時，這些同學你那時候還不知道在哪裡，說難聽一點是細胞還未形成」。<br />\n<br />\n對於政改方案當年在立法會遭否決，他則指立會要配合政府施政，又批評有議員不論對錯「拉布」，令措施不能通過，要負很大責任，「你幾乎百分之百的反對，它（政府）怎麼辦」，但他不評論時任特首梁振英的施政表現，稱要留待市民評價。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180219/57851011\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180219%2F57851011&d=dPt5hoR%2F8%2FipJ5OUgle%2BkIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=34efb463\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180219%2F57851011&h=40a2e2e4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180219/57851011</a>"},{"pid":"c391c23722ff45c6d9095cc4632a7ec17c115e4d","tid":565791,"uid":36238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T10:36:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"631e87bc40adb0eb4ff578d3b564ff3f1f40d9af","tid":565791,"uid":157362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T10:37:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b6c7825afa8e5a2d7e8668b95e50e86a75506f1f","tid":565791,"uid":37528,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"631e87bc40adb0eb4ff578d3b564ff3f1f40d9af","tid":565791,"uid":157362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T10:37:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T10:38:19.000Z","msg":"好似係畜牲黎"},{"pid":"6b39cd5039b6746fe2520a7338a51e16679e0918","tid":565791,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T10:39:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a06087fa7884107095528802312d5054ea3d071f","tid":565791,"uid":52215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T10:40:48.000Z","msg":"諗起黃子華棟篤笑秋前算帳<br />\n講起張浚生，成日去舞會識人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f42014690b78b837be16b1cd44fa64bc2c07edc1","tid":565791,"uid":35221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T10:43:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.pn